      "type": "description",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Soient $n,p \\in \\N$. On note $\\Gamma_n^p$ le nombre de $n$-uplets\n$(x_1,\\dots, x_n) \\in \\N^n$ tels que $x_1 + \\dots + x_n = p$.",
        "html": "<p>Soient <span class=\"math inline\">\\(n,p \\in \\N\\)</span>. On note <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(\\Gamma_n^p\\)</span> le nombre de <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(n\\)</span>-uplets <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\((x_1,\\dots, x_n) \\in \\N^n\\)</span> tels que <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(x_1 + \\dots + x_n = p\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "c5a594b7-5f81-4960-8e95-7da0055e6a05",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "D{\\'e}terminer $\\Gamma_n^0$, $\\Gamma_n^1$, $\\Gamma_n^2$, $\\Gamma_2^n$.",
        "html": "<p>D<span>é</span>terminer <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(\\Gamma_n^0\\)</span>, <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(\\Gamma_n^1\\)</span>, <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(\\Gamma_n^2\\)</span>, <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(\\Gamma_2^n\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "e39423ce-c70d-4517-bfdc-7933a29c3736",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "D{\\'e}montrer que $\\Gamma_{n+1}^{p+1} = \\Gamma_{n+1}^p + \\Gamma_n^{p+1}$\n    (on classera les $(n+1)$-uplets tels que $x_1 + \\dots + x_{n+1} = p + 1$\n    suivant que $x_1 = 0$ ou non).",
        "html": "<p>D<span>é</span>montrer que <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(\\Gamma_{n+1}^{p+1} = \\Gamma_{n+1}^p +\n\\Gamma_n^{p+1}\\)</span> (on classera les <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\((n+1)\\)</span>-uplets tels que <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(x_1 + \\dots + x_{n+1} = p + 1\\)</span> suivant que\n<span class=\"math inline\">\\(x_1 = 0\\)</span> ou non).</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "e0e9b805-d213-4801-8bf7-16c8758ffebe",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "En d{\\'e}duire que $\\Gamma_n^p = C_{n+p-1}^p$.",
        "html": "<p>En d<span>é</span>duire que <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\Gamma_n^p =\nC_{n+p-1}^p\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
