        "html": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\Gamma_n^0 = 1\\)</span>, <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(\\Gamma_n^1 = n\\)</span>, <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(\\Gamma_n^2 = \\frac {n(n+1)}2\\)</span>, <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(\\Gamma_2^n = n+1\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    }
